  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim of this randomized double-blinded study is to determine whether transition to
      propofol for 3 min at the end of sevoﬂurane anaesthesia reduces the incidence of EA in
      children undergoing genito-urinary paediatric surgeries.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
